    {
      "id": "https://boingboing.net/2026/02/25/john-shirleys-guide-to-wrecking-your-career-in-science-fiction.html",
      "url": "https://boingboing.net/2026/02/25/john-shirleys-guide-to-wrecking-your-career-in-science-fiction.html",
      "title": "[Boing Boing] John Shirley's guide to wrecking your career in science fiction",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/john-shirley.jpg?fit=1200%2C669&quality=60&ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/02/25/john-shirleys-guide-to-wrecking-your-career-in-science-fiction.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"John Shirley&#039;s guide to wrecking your career in science fiction\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"669\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/john-shirley.jpg?fit=1200%2C669&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1200\" /></a><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p><em>\"I'm growing up in public, growing up in public,<br />growing up in public — with my pants down.\"</em><br />— Lou Reed</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Kamikaze, streaking from the sky! Crash and burn!</p>\n<p>Thus, the fanatical rage-fueled Kamikaze flight of yours truly in 1976, as I pilot the Japanese Zero of my career, teeth-gritting as I arc my aircraft down to destroy itself on the rusting plates of the steampunkish Jules-Vernean battleship that was science-fiction. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/02/25/john-shirleys-guide-to-wrecking-your-career-in-science-fiction.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/02/25/john-shirleys-guide-to-wrecking-your-career-in-science-fiction.html\">John Shirley&#039;s guide to wrecking your career in science fiction</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
